{
  "verses": [
    {
      "n": 14,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Divisimts Kasas/ un di-\nwidesimts Ahſchus / diwisimts\nAwis/ un diwideſimts Aunus.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 15,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Trihsdefinitis ſihdoſchas\nRameetu-Mahtes/ar fatweemKu-\nmeteem/tſchetrdefinitis Gohwis/\nun definitis Wehrſchus / diwide-\nmits Ehſeta-Mahtes/ un definitis\nRuuetus.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 16,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un dewe tohs ſawo Kalpu\nRohkā/ iſkatru Pulku fewischki/\nun fazzija us fatweem Kalpeem:\nEita juhs man papreeſchu / un\npametteet Starpibu starp tkwee-\nnu Pulku.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 17,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un wiꞥſch pawehſeja tam pahrwedde tohs pahr to Uppi,\npirmajam/ fazzidans: Kad Ee-\nsaws mans Brahlis tewfastaps/ bij/ bet Jehkabs palikke ween\nun tew waizahs / un fazzijhs: pats.\nRam tu peederr/ un us kurren tu\neij/ un kam peederr ſchee/kas tawā\nPreeſschā?\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 18,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tad buhs tero fazzijht: Tee\npeederr tawam Kalpam Jehka-\nbam/ tas fuhta fatwam Kungam\nEesawain Dahwanu/ un redſi /\nwiꞥſch pats irr arridsan pakkat\nmums.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 19,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un wiꞥſch pawehſeja ar-\nridsan tam ohtrain/ un tam tre-\nſcham/ un wiffeem/ kas tohs Loh-\npus dsinne / fazzidans: Pehz\nſcheem Wahrdeem buhs jums\nfazzijht us Eesawu/kad juhs to at-\nraſſeet.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 20,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un jums buhs arridsan\nfazzijht: Rangi / taws Kalps\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 1,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Jehkabs irr pakkat muns/ jo\nwiꞥſch fazzija : Es fameerina-\nſchu winna Waigu ar ſcho Dah-\nwanu/ kas man papreeſchu eet/\nun pehz to redſejchu es winna\nWaigu/ kas finna/ wiꞥſch man-\nnis peeneus.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 21,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tad aifgahje nu ta Dah-\nwana/ winnam papreeſchu/ be-\nwiꞥſch pats palikke to Nakti pee\nfatwa Pulka.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 22,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un wiꞥſch zehluhs tann\nNakti / un nehme ſawas Diw-\nSeewas/ un ſawas diwi Kalpo-\nnes / un ſawas weenpadefmite\nBehrnus / un gahje pee tah-\nPahrzelffanas-Weetas Jabaks.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 23,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un wiꞥſch nehme tohs u-\nnes / un ſawas diwi Kalpo-\nBehrnus / un gahje pee tah-\nPahrzelffanas-Weetas Jabaks.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 24,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tad zihnijahsweens Wihr-\nar to/ kamehr Deena ſahze auſt\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 25,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un kad tas redſeja / ka ta-\nwinnu ne pahrſpehja / atſkah-\ntas winna Ziskas Lohzekli/ ta ka-\ntas Lohzeklis pee Jehkaba Ziska-\nzihkſtoht iggreeſahs.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 26,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un tas fazzija : Palai-\nmann/ jo Gaifina jaw rahdahs\nbet wiꞥſch atbilduja / es tew u-\npalaidsſchu/jatu mann ne fwheht\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 27,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un tas fazzija us winnu\nKaſirr taws Wahrdṣ? un wiꞥſc-\nfazzija/Jehkabs.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 28,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tad tazzija tas: Tawa-\nWahrdam ne buhs wairs Je-\nkabs fauktam tapt / bet Israels\njo tu effi zihntjees ar Deewn u-\nar zi\n"
    }
  ],
  "confidence": "high",
  "notes": ""
}
